SETPOS [-108 50] SETH 0 PD
REPEAT 36 [FD 5 RT 10]
PU SETSH 30 SETC 11
REPEAT 10 [FD 10 RT 18 STAMP]
HT SETPOS [-89 65]
SETSH 42 STAMP
PU SETX XCOR + 22
STAMP HT
END

TO START 
LOADSH "ALPHA
CS SETBG 1
SETCURSOR [7 0] SETTC [1 11] TYPE [* MATCHING SMALL *]
SETTC 1
PRLE FACE
MAKE "T 0
MAKE "F 0
HA
LABEL "START
MAKE "V 28 + RANDOM 26
PU SETPC 15 SETPOS [-15 35] SETSH :V
STAMP SETC 0
MAKE "T :T + 1
SETPOS [-100 0] SETSH 26 SETC 3
CATCH "HOME [INPUT]
IF :F = CHAR 189 [GO "END]
CHANGE.COLOR 15 0
IF :T < 5 [GO "START]
LABEL "END
HT CS
END

TO SOUND 
